subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Lorena Ochoa shot a six-under-par 66 to take a three-stroke lead in the Navistar L.P.G.A. Classic in Prattville, Ala., leaving 14-year-old Alexis Thompson eight strokes behind.
